## Main statements

* `CategoryTheory.PGrpd.isPullback_forgetToGrpd_forgetToCat` -
  the functor `PGrpd.forgetToGrpd` is the pullback
  along `Grpd.forgetToCat` of `PCat.forgetToCat`.

